[Thank you very much to Dr. Heinzpeter Schwermer for pointing out my error in calculation/interpretation of the data in the excess mortality report. My apologies for any confusion caused by my error. While it is embarrassing to have made that error, it is nice to know the report is being read and given the opportunity to correct that error for our subscribers.

I would also like to thank Dr. Heinzpeter Schwermer for sending a link to the Euro MOMO website and highly recommend our readers to link over to the website. The graphs and maps are impressive for following the excess mortality impact of the pandemic in 24 European countries. - Mod.MPP]

